Subject: Re: [T2] Tranny innerchange

I shoehorned the powerstroke in too, the way I did it was much like
installing a bug engine, I clearanced the mounting area, and the starter,
then I hung the tranny, without the engine, and worked it in at a great
angle, just like a bug engine, it was not really that bad..

I will be dropping the engine to add the Turbo this winter, and plan to
install an 091 to use all the extra power, I thinkl the extra gear will be
nice with boost.
